message:
Hello everyone!

I am looking for a lady person to sublease for me as soon as possible!
I currently live at the Lighthouse, which is a house filled with wonderful God-loving ladies. The house is located two blocks from the campus connector and about three blocks away from campus!

The rent would be about $400, which includes utilities and communal food. I lived at the Lighthouse last year and it was a beautiful experience!
Please private message me for more details! And if you know of anyone who might be interested, please let them know!
